## Overview

CRforDR is a Mathematica-Package which implements a Complete Reduction for RPiSigma-rings. It is 

## Requirements

CRforDR is developed and tested for Wolfram Mathematica 14.3, but should work on any resent version of Mathematica.

## Installation

Clone Repository and move the directory into one of the directories in $Path where Mathematica can find it. 

## Documentation

See the Mathematica-Notebook Examples.nb. 

